cause_of_action: Dispute over Treaty No. 7 provisions and distribution of settlement funds.
relevant_rule: Section 17(1) of the Federal Court Act
procedure_steps: Motion to strike out plaintiffs' Statement of Claim filed by both Crown and Youngman et al., citing Rule 419 and jurisdictional concerns.
decision_reasoning: The Statement of Claim should not be struck out as it raises legitimate legal issues and factual disputes requiring trial resolution.
result_details: Applications dismissed; case proceeds to trial to resolve substantive issues.
